text: Jeff Wiska (born October 17, 1959) is a former American football guard. He played for the Michigan Panthers in 1984, the Oakland Invaders in 1985, the Cleveland Browns in 1986 and for the Miami Dolphins in 1987. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:American football guards Category:Michigan State Spartans football players Category:Michigan Panthers players Category:Oakland Invaders players Category:Cleveland Browns players Category:Miami Dolphins players
